410
00:20:33,050 --> 00:20:34,940
My grandma was on the boat too.

411
00:20:35,230 --> 00:20:37,310
I wanted to catch her.

412
00:20:37,460 --> 00:20:39,980
But she kept pushing me

413
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:40,800
and asked me

414
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:43,110
