425
00:21:14,950 --> 00:21:16,560
who has no blood ties.

426
00:21:16,870 --> 00:21:18,380
In this fire,

427
00:21:18,850 --> 00:21:19,730
the grandma died from

428
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:20,880
trying to save her.

429
00:21:21,130 --> 00:21:22,220
The media are looking for

430
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,150
her parents everywhere,

431
00:21:23,420 --> 00:21:24,750
but they can't find them.

432
00:21:25,460 --> 00:21:26,900
How can people who deliberately abandon

433
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:28,770
