434
00:21:29,330 --> 00:21:30,140
Yes.

435
00:21:30,590 --> 00:21:31,830
She's so pitiful.

436
00:21:32,580 --> 00:21:33,940
She's so young.

437
00:21:33,980 --> 00:21:34,860
What should she do in the future?

438
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:35,520
All right.

439
00:21:35,550 --> 00:21:36,820
Don't be sad here.

440
00:21:36,850 --> 00:21:37,500
Prepare the medicine.

441
00:21:37,520 --> 00:21:38,560
Treat her quickly.

442
00:21:45,220 --> 00:21:51,250
