463
00:22:12,550 --> 00:22:15,270
[Zone 16, Observation Ward]

464
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:13,820
People are making donations

465
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:14,700
and helping Orange

466
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:15,560
to look for her mother.

467
00:22:17,290 --> 00:22:18,180
She abandoned

468
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:19,310
