469
00:22:19,510 --> 00:22:20,910
Why do you want her back?

470
00:22:21,630 --> 00:22:22,510
She doesn't

471
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:23,630
deserve to be a mother.

472
00:22:24,060 --> 00:22:25,480
Without her,

473
00:22:25,750 --> 00:22:27,020
Orange may be better off

474
00:22:27,050 --> 00:22:28,010
in a new life.

475
00:22:52,310 --> 00:22:52,950
Thank you.

476
00:22:53,740 --> 00:22:54,660
What brings you here?

477
00:22:56,420 --> 00:22:57,580
When I found her in the fire,

478
00:22:57,780 --> 00:22:58,980
