00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:54,080
I'll go.

561
00:28:08,100 --> 00:28:09,100
I'm sorry.

562
00:28:09,790 --> 00:28:10,830
This Saturday...

563
00:28:11,380 --> 00:28:12,260
It's OK.

564
00:28:16,450 --> 00:28:21,760
[Emergency Ward]

