00:28:25,980 --> 00:28:28,020
Qin is so elegant.

566
00:28:29,070 --> 00:28:30,110
Thank you, Aunt.

567
00:28:31,560 --> 00:28:32,280
By the way,

568
00:28:32,470 --> 00:28:34,030
